{"article_id":"IimE1qVs5YUS7cZ7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Like an HR meeting convened in hell ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"the whole Ukraine impeachment saga is boring , hard to understand ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and apparently goes on for eternity .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"It never ends .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Washington endured ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"and the rest of America ignored ,","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"yet another round of it on Wednesday .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"The hearings consumed virtually every hour of Wednesday 's available daylight","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"and elevated to international celebrity this country 's current ambassador to the European Union , a man","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"called Gordon Sondland .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"In contrast to other recent witnesses , Sondland was n't obviously hostile to the administration .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"In fact , he was appointed directly by President Trump .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"He was also a major Trump donor .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"So ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"given those two facts ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Sondland 's opening statement this morning initially looked like a complete disaster for the administration .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"KEN STARR ON IMPEACHMENT HEARINGS SO FAR :","depth":3},{"id":17,"text":"WE 'RE 'NOWHERE CLOSE ' TO IMPEACHABLE OFFENSES","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"Gordon Sondland , U.S. ambassador to European Union :","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"I know","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"that members of this committee frequently framed these complicated issues in the form of a simple question ,","depth":14},{"id":21,"text":"`` Was there a quid pro quo ? ''","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"As I testified previously ,","depth":15},{"id":23,"text":"with regard to the requested White House call and the White House meeting ,","depth":15},{"id":24,"text":"the answer is , `` Yes . ''","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"So that 's how the morning began .","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"`` The answer is , 'Yes , ' ''","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"said Gordon Sondland .","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"`` There was a quid pro quo . ''","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"And not only that ,","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"he explained ,","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"pretty much everybody knew about it .","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"Sondland :","depth":15},{"id":33,"text":"Everyone was in the loop .","depth":15},{"id":34,"text":"It was no secret .","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"Everyone was informed via email on July 19th , days before the presidential call .","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"Holy smokes !","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"For a moment there , it looked like case closed .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"The final ignominious end of the Trump presidency , the one","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that our perpetually excitable friends in the news media have been confidently predicting day after rage-filled day , for more than three years now .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"The last meltdown","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"-- the great Orange Hindenburg finally bursts into flames .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"In TV studios across midtown Manhattan , cable news contributors struggled to hold back tears of joy .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"And then Adam Schiff took the microphone .","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"Schiff , as the ringmaster of this particular circus , was determined to bring it to its final theatrical close .","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"`` Tell us , ''","depth":17},{"id":46,"text":"Adam Schiff said ,","depth":17},{"id":47,"text":"`` about President Trump 's deal with Ukraine","depth":17},{"id":48,"text":"to investigate Joe Biden in return for foreign aid . ''","depth":17},{"id":49,"text":"It was the moment","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"Democrats had been waiting for .","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"But ,","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"when it finally arrived ,","depth":16},{"id":53,"text":"Gordon Sondland would n't read from the script .","depth":16},{"id":54,"text":"Adam Schiff , chairman of the House Intelligence Committee :","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"Though President Trump claimed to you","depth":18},{"id":56,"text":"there was no quid pro quo ,","depth":18},{"id":57,"text":"he also made it clear to you in that call","depth":18},{"id":58,"text":"that President Zelensky had to `` clear things up","depth":19},{"id":59,"text":"and do it in public . ''","depth":19},{"id":60,"text":"You do n't have a reason","depth":17},{"id":61,"text":"to dispute","depth":18},{"id":62,"text":"that 's what you told --","depth":18},{"id":63,"text":"Sondland :","depth":15},{"id":64,"text":"I do n't have any reason","depth":16},{"id":65,"text":"to dispute the `` clear things up and do it in public . ''","depth":16},{"id":66,"text":"What I 'm trying to be very clear about was President Trump never told me directly","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"that the aid was tied to that statement .","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"Schiff :","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"But in that same conversation","depth":17},{"id":70,"text":"you had with him about the aid , about the quid pro quo ,","depth":17},{"id":71,"text":"he told you","depth":17},{"id":72,"text":"that President Zelensky had to `` clear things up","depth":18},{"id":73,"text":"and do it in public , ''","depth":18},{"id":74,"text":"correct ?","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"Sondland :","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"I did not have a conversation with him about the aid .","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"I had a conversation with him","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"as referenced in my text about quid pro quo .","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"Schiff :","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"Well , the quid pro quo","depth":16},{"id":81,"text":"you were discussing","depth":16},{"id":82,"text":"was over the aid , correct ?","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"Sondland :","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"No .","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"President Trump --","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"when I asked him the open-ended question ,","depth":17},{"id":87,"text":"as I testified previously ,","depth":17},{"id":88,"text":"`` What do you want from Ukraine , ''","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"his answer was ,","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"`` I want nothing .","depth":17},{"id":91,"text":"I want no quid pro quo .","depth":18},{"id":92,"text":"Tell Zelensky to do the right thing . ''","depth":18},{"id":93,"text":"That 's all","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"I got from President Trump .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"So , they pushed him ,","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"and they pushed him ,","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"and they pushed him again ,","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"but Gordon Sondland would not , in the end , mouth Adam Schiff 's talking points .","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"Well , why not ?","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"Maybe because he did n't have any evidence","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"that they were true .","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"As Sondland conceded in the exchange with Congressman Michael Turner ,","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"his assessment of any deals","depth":16},{"id":104,"text":"Trump may have struck with Ukraine","depth":16},{"id":105,"text":"was based mostly on assumptions .","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"U.S. Rep. Mike Turner , R-Ohio :","depth":18},{"id":107,"text":"No one on this planet told you","depth":20},{"id":108,"text":"that President Trump was tying aid to investigations","depth":20},{"id":109,"text":"- yes or no ?","depth":19},{"id":110,"text":"Turner :","depth":18},{"id":111,"text":"So , you really have no testimony today","depth":19},{"id":112,"text":"that ties President Trump to a scheme","depth":20},{"id":113,"text":"to withhold aid from Ukraine in exchange for these investigations ?","depth":20},{"id":114,"text":"This is tiresome .","depth":18},{"id":115,"text":"And of course , we apologize for it","depth":19},{"id":116,"text":"as we have in nights ' past .","depth":19},{"id":117,"text":"But","depth":18},{"id":118,"text":"since it 's happening ,","depth":19},{"id":119,"text":"we feel duty-bound to explain it .","depth":19},{"id":120,"text":"So a presumption .","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"Now , some presumptions are correct .","depth":17},{"id":122,"text":"Others are laughably wrong .","depth":17},{"id":123,"text":"But one thing","depth":17},{"id":124,"text":"a presumption definitely is n't is evidence .","depth":17},{"id":125,"text":"You ca n't overturn an election","depth":17},{"id":126,"text":"based on a presumption .","depth":17},{"id":127,"text":"You ca n't stage an impeachment on presumptions .","depth":17},{"id":128,"text":"You need facts","depth":18},{"id":129,"text":"to do that .","depth":18},{"id":130,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"as the day went on ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Sondland introduced a new fact :","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"the president ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"Gordon Sondland told us ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"had told him explicitly","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"that he , in fact , did n't want a quid pro quo with Ukraine .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"U.S. Rep Jim Jordan , R-Ohio :","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"You said to the president of the United States ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"`` What do you want from Ukraine ? ''","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"The president :","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"`` I want nothing .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"I want no quid pro quo .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"I want Zelensky to do the right thing .","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"I want him to do what he ran on . ''","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"Why did n't you put that statement in your opening statement ?","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"you said","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"you could n't fit it in .","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"Is that right ?","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Instead , we might be here for 46 minutes instead of 45 minutes ?","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"It 's a fair question , actually .","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"So why was n't that fact","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"-- and it 's not a small point , by the way .","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"It 's the point","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"on which the entire impeachment hangs .","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"Why was n't that point included in Sondland 's opening statement ?","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"Well , we do n't know , really ,","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"but here 's one possible explanation .","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"The statement was likely drafted by Sondland 's legal team .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"All four of his attorneys","depth":15},{"id":161,"text":"-- it turns out ,","depth":16},{"id":162,"text":"because we checked --","depth":16},{"id":163,"text":"are Democratic donors .","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"The man","depth":17},{"id":165,"text":"seated next to Gordon Sondland today during the hearing ,","depth":17},{"id":166,"text":"that would be a man","depth":17},{"id":167,"text":"called Robert Luskin .","depth":17},{"id":168,"text":"He has given over $ 130,000 to the Democrats over the years .","depth":15},{"id":169,"text":"Luskin also represented the FBI informant , Stefan Halper during the Russia hoax not too long ago .","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"Yes , a lot of people in Washington despise Donald Trump .","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"But still , to this moment , nobody can prove a crime .","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"So is it possible that someone like Luskin was thinking about more than his client 's personal interests in this case ?","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"Could impeaching public enemy No . 1 have crossed his mind ?","depth":14},{"id":174,"text":"We do n't know ,","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"but it does n't seem implausible .","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"We should also point out something","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"that the press conveniently overlooked in its analysis Wednesday for the most part .","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"Gordon Sondland and his family have been under intense political pressure","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"-- in some cases , scary political pressure --","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"from the left for weeks .","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"Protesters have swarmed Gordon Sondland and his family in public .","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"Democratic politicians have endorsed boycotts","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"-- pushed boycotts --","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"of his businesses , his livelihood .","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"In other words , the left has been working the refs .","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"And that should n't surprise you","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"because , for the left , this is total war .","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"And yet , in this one case , it did n't quite work .","depth":8},{"id":189,"text":"By the close of business today , we were back right where we were","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"when the Ukraine circus started .","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"In fact , we 're back where we were on November 9 , 2016 .","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"Yes , a lot of people in Washington despise Donald Trump .","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"But still , to this moment , nobody can prove a crime .","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"Do n't tell the press , though .","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"They 're celebrating","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"as if someone did .","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"Jeffrey Toobin , CNN legal analyst :","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"Now we know","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"that every fantasy","depth":13},{"id":200,"text":"about how corrupt this administration was","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"is actually true .","depth":12},{"id":202,"text":"Brian Williams , MSNBC anchor :","depth":15},{"id":203,"text":"For our live coverage of the blowtorch testimony this morning from Gordon Sondland -- [ he ] turns out to be the guy","depth":16},{"id":204,"text":"that has offered the most stunning testimony .","depth":16},{"id":205,"text":"Ari Melber , MSNBC anchor :","depth":15},{"id":206,"text":"In addition to that and the bombshells","depth":17},{"id":207,"text":"we 've heard about ,","depth":17},{"id":208,"text":"this was an IED from Mr. Sondland .","depth":16},{"id":209,"text":"Nicolle Wallace , MSNBC anchor :","depth":16},{"id":210,"text":"As you said ,","depth":17},{"id":211,"text":"taking a blowtorch to even the defense","depth":20},{"id":212,"text":"Donald Trump has offered","depth":20},{"id":213,"text":"-- we do n't say this very often anymore ,","depth":20},{"id":214,"text":"because it 's rarely true ,","depth":20},{"id":215,"text":"but I think","depth":19},{"id":216,"text":"today changed everything .","depth":19},{"id":217,"text":"So , you heard it .","depth":16},{"id":218,"text":"`` Bombshells , IEDs , blowtorches . ''","depth":16},{"id":219,"text":"Who writes the metaphors for these hair hats ?","depth":14},{"id":220,"text":"It sounds like Wednesday 's hearing was taking place in ISIS territory , in the caliphate .","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"But the really telling line comes from the CNN legal analyst","depth":14},{"id":222,"text":"-- and we 're quoting now :","depth":15},{"id":223,"text":"`` Every fantasy","depth":17},{"id":224,"text":"about how corrupt this administration was","depth":17},{"id":225,"text":"is actually true . ''","depth":16},{"id":226,"text":"So pause for a minute","depth":14},{"id":227,"text":"and think about what he 's telling you .","depth":14},{"id":228,"text":"All of the fantasies","depth":18},{"id":229,"text":"the press has held","depth":19},{"id":230,"text":"without evidence","depth":19},{"id":231,"text":"are true","depth":17},{"id":232,"text":"based on testimony from another person","depth":17},{"id":233,"text":"who does n't have evidence .","depth":17},{"id":234,"text":"So you remember the Russia collusion story ?","depth":16},{"id":235,"text":"Remember Stormy Daniels ?","depth":17},{"id":236,"text":"Remember every totally baseless","depth":19},{"id":237,"text":"-- and in some cases , insane --","depth":19},{"id":238,"text":"allegation","depth":19},{"id":239,"text":"that people like CNN 's legal analyst Toobin invented and promoted and used","depth":20},{"id":240,"text":"to try to affect elections","depth":21},{"id":241,"text":"and , in so doing , destroyed lives ?","depth":21},{"id":242,"text":"Well , they 're telling us","depth":17},{"id":243,"text":"that all of them were true","depth":17},{"id":244,"text":"because of our presumptions .","depth":16},{"id":245,"text":"That 's the most revealing thing in all of this .","depth":15},{"id":246,"text":"From the beginning , Washington has had `` presumptions '' about what the new president was like , about what policies voters were allowed to choose .","depth":13},{"id":247,"text":"Voters were n't allowed to end foreign wars","depth":16},{"id":248,"text":"by casting a ballot ,","depth":16},{"id":249,"text":"or to put America first ,","depth":16},{"id":250,"text":"or to secure America 's borders .","depth":16},{"id":251,"text":"That 's not on the table .","depth":15},{"id":252,"text":"Those are n't menu options .","depth":15},{"id":253,"text":"This is n't a real democracy ,","depth":11},{"id":254,"text":"according to the people","depth":12},{"id":255,"text":"who administer the democracy .","depth":12},{"id":256,"text":"And , by the way , that ought to make you nervous .","depth":10},{"id":257,"text":"You come to Washington , the city","depth":14},{"id":258,"text":"that 's in charge of our democracy ,","depth":14},{"id":259,"text":"and no one believes in it ?","depth":13},{"id":260,"text":"You 're like --","depth":14},{"id":261,"text":"if you showed up in Detroit","depth":16},{"id":262,"text":"and everyone 's driving a Japanese car ,","depth":16},{"id":263,"text":"would it make you nervous ?","depth":15},{"id":264,"text":"It would .","depth":13},{"id":265,"text":"And they do n't believe in it .","depth":11},{"id":266,"text":"And so , what they 're really saying to voters is you ca n't actually make changes to American policies , the ones","depth":12},{"id":267,"text":"that we support .","depth":12},{"id":268,"text":"All","depth":14},{"id":269,"text":"you 're allowed to do","depth":14},{"id":270,"text":"is rubber-stamp the current status quo , the one","depth":14},{"id":271,"text":"that enriches private equity managers and defense contractors and parasites in the vast federal bureaucracy","depth":15},{"id":272,"text":"-- our donors and friends .","depth":15},{"id":273,"text":"Other than that , shut up","depth":13},{"id":274,"text":"and obey .","depth":13},{"id":275,"text":"So that 's their program .","depth":10},{"id":276,"text":"And maybe they 'll succeed in the end .","depth":11},{"id":277,"text":"Maybe they 'll remove the president .","depth":11},{"id":278,"text":"OK.","depth":10},{"id":279,"text":"What then ?","depth":10},{"id":280,"text":"Well , Washington will celebrate , of course .","depth":10},{"id":281,"text":"But will they have learned anything from the exercise ?","depth":10},{"id":282,"text":"Will the 2016 election have changed their minds or their priorities at all , in any way ?","depth":12},{"id":283,"text":"Or will they continue to console themselves with the whole thing was just some weird aberration","depth":14},{"id":284,"text":"run by Russia and racists in the heartland .","depth":14},{"id":285,"text":"Something","depth":14},{"id":286,"text":"that they can safely ignore","depth":15},{"id":287,"text":"and return to a kind of arrangement","depth":16},{"id":288,"text":"that looks very much like 1998","depth":17},{"id":289,"text":"-- or 1978 for that matter .","depth":17},{"id":290,"text":"Well , you know the answer to that .","depth":11},{"id":291,"text":"If the people in charge were capable of learning anything ,","depth":10},{"id":292,"text":"our country would n't look","depth":11},{"id":293,"text":"like it does today .","depth":11},{"id":294,"text":"Adapted from Tucker Carlson 's monologue from `` Tucker Carlson Tonight '' on Nov. 20 , 2019 .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":589,"left":310,"right":588,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":310,"left":298,"right":309,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":0,"right":297,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":297,"left":296,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":296,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":309,"left":300,"right":308,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":299,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":299,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":7,"right":307,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":307,"left":301,"right":306,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":303,"right":305,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":10,"right":302,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":13,"right":304,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":304,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":588,"left":587,"right":294,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":587,"left":16,"right":586,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":586,"left":17,"right":585,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":585,"left":467,"right":584,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":467,"left":436,"right":466,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":436,"left":421,"right":435,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":421,"left":329,"right":420,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":329,"left":18,"right":328,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":328,"left":319,"right":327,"re